---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  title="CV | Dr. Haitham A. El-Ghareeb"
  description="A provisional academic profile page for Dr. Haitham A. El-Ghareeb"
>
  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="shell hero">
      <p class="hero__eyebrow">CV</p>
      <h1 class="hero__title">Provisional academic profile</h1>
      <p class="hero__lead">
        This initial CV page offers a structured overview of the intended academic profile and
        will later be expanded with verified degrees, positions, teaching, publications, and
        institutional links.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="shell section">
      <div class="grid-two">
        <article class="content-card">
          <p class="content-card__meta">Current description</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">General academic orientation</h2>
          <p>
            The present project indicates a scholarly profile that combines academic work,
            research activity, editorial interests, and organized digital publication.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="content-card">
          <p class="content-card__meta">Planned scope</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">What this page will eventually include</h2>
          <p>
            Future updates will add qualifications, appointments, teaching roles, reviewing work,
            publications, and external academic profile references.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="shell notice-card">
      <h2 class="section-title">Details pending later revision</h2>
      <ul class="list-clean">
        <li>Academic degrees and formal qualifications.</li>
        <li>Professional, teaching, and research appointments.</li>
        <li>Selected publications and academic profile links.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
